[{:itonami.blueprint/id "cloud-itonami-isic-4510"
  :itonami.blueprint/name "Sale of motor vehicles"
  :itonami.blueprint/isic-rev5 "4510"
  :itonami.blueprint/domain :automotive/vehicle-sales
  :itonami.blueprint/license "AGPL-3.0-or-later"
  :itonami.blueprint/social-impact [:consumer-protection :transparency :road-safety]
  :itonami.blueprint/governor :vehicle-sale-governor
  :itonami.blueprint/robotics false
  :itonami.blueprint/required-technologies [:identity :forms :dmn :bpmn :audit-ledger]
  :itonami.blueprint/optional-technologies []
  :itonami.blueprint/status :public-oss
  :itonami.blueprint/maturity :implemented
  :itonami.blueprint/implemented-slice
  "VehicleSale-LLM ⊣ VehicleSaleGovernor, langgraph-clj StateGraph
  (langgraph.graph, vehiclesale.operation/build: intake -> advise ->
  govern -> decide -+-> commit / request-approval -> commit / hold),
  interrupt-before #{:request-approval} + in-memory checkpointer for
  real human-in-the-loop resume (title officer approves/rejects), and
  an append-only audit ledger (vehiclesale.store/ledger +
  append-ledger!, MemStore + DatomicStore parity). The Governor
  (src/vehiclesale/policy.cljc) runs 8 checks in priority order --
  5 HARD (rbac, lien-clearance-gate, odometer-disclosure-gate,
  source-provenance-gate, licensed-disclosure) a human approver cannot
  override, plus 3 SOFT/always-escalate (confidence floor,
  salvage-title-gate, dispute-request) that route to a human reviewer.
  Deliberately narrow scope: this actor lists, discloses and confirms
  sale DECISIONS only -- there is no field anywhere in the schema for
  payment processing, escrow, or funds transfer (docs/adr/0001,
  src/vehiclesale/store.cljc). Provenance is limited to real, citable
  public reference sources (src/vehiclesale/facts.cljc: the DOJ NMVTIS
  one-report-per-VIN gateway, NHTSA recalls) plus one structural class,
  :operator-licensed-dmv-feed, for operator-registered state DMV
  title/lien access (no nationwide free source exists for that data).
  Test suite (clojure -M:dev:test) and clj-kondo (clojure -M:lint) both
  green; governance-doc set (LICENSE, GOVERNANCE.md, CONTRIBUTING.md,
  SECURITY.md, CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md), docs/ (business model, design ADR,
  operator guide) and CI (.github/workflows/ci.yml, lint+test,
  sibling-checkout pattern for :local/root deps) already present."
  :db/id -1}]
